data.description: Breathtaking views in every direction! This stunning ranch style home offers 3,249 sq ft sits on .47 acre, with 4 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms and a 3 car garage.  The open concept living is perfect for entertaining as well as everyday living.  The updated kitchen has a huge seated bar area as well as a 5 burner gas range.  Both bathrooms have been tastefully updated.  The primary suite includes a huge bonus room as well as a step-in shower, soaking tub, huge walk-in closet with a custom shoe rack. The living area is enormous and also has a cozy gas fireplace, hardwood floors, incredible views  with tons of space for family and friends.  Located in view of the 17th hole of the golf course, this property is Western Colorado living at its finest. Meticulously maintained and is ready for new owners!
